Package mca.io

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ChunkLocation
    A class that holds information about the location of a chunk, such as it's byte offset within the .mca file and the number of sectors associated with the assigned chunk.
    ChunkLocationTable
    A ChunkLocationTable holds the references to all ChunkLocation objects.
    ChunkTimestamp
    A class that contains information about when a chunk was last modified.
    ChunkTimestampTable
    A ChunkLocationTable holds the references to all ChunkTimestamp objects.
    MCAReader
    An MCAReader handles all the byte reading operations and is able to construct an instance of a MCAFile object from that data.
    RawChunkData
    A class that contains the raw byte data of a chunk and contains methods to navigate or decompress that data in order to prepare it for the conversion to an NBT tag.
    RawChunkDataReader
    An RawChunkDataReader handles all the byte reading operations and is able to construct an instance of a RawChunkData object from that data.
